---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import speaker1 from "../assets/images/Speaker_DavidBenjamin.jpg";
import speaker2 from "../assets/images/Speaker_Mahendra.jpg";
import venue1 from "../assets/images/OPCJ-dining-newoakbar.jpg";
import venue2 from "../assets/images/OPCJ-dining-newoakbar2.jpg";
import venue3 from "../assets/images/OPCJ-dining-Oakroom-Restaurant-Bar.jpg";
import venue4 from "../assets/images/OPCJ-Flavour-of-Batavia.webp";
import venue5 from "../assets/images/OPCJ-lounge.jpg";
import venue6 from "../assets/images/OPCJ-The-Batavia-Pour.webp";
---

<Layout>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 md:gap-20">
    <Header />

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <h2>
          Join us for the first ever dedicated Vonage RCS event in Jakarta 
          and see what the future of business messaging looks like, live.
        </h2>
        <p>
          As business messaging continues to evolve, RCS is emerging as a
          powerful new channel for brands to deliver richer, more interactive
          customer experiences - delivered straight to the native messaging app
          - no extra downloads, no friction. This invite-only, executive-level
          session brings together experts from Vonage to share global
          perspectives, APAC readiness insights, and a live demonstration of RCS
          in action. Attendees will gain practical clarity on how RCS is shaping
          the future of customer engagement and what it means for their 2026
          messaging roadmap.
        </p>
        <h3 class="mt-10 text-balance">
          Future of Messaging: How RCS Will Transform Brand Engagement in APAC.
        </h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Messaging is entering a new era.</li>
          <li>
            RCS is more than the evolution of SMS. It enables branded,
            interactive, and conversational experiences that combine the reach
            of messaging with the richness of app-like engagement.
          </li>
          <li>
            With APAC entering a critical stage of RCS adoption, this session
            will help you understand where the market is heading and how to
            prepare for what's next.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-6 md:gap-y-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="uppercase">What you'll gain from this session.</h3>
              <p>
                This session is designed to give you clear, practical insight
                into how RCS is changing business messaging — and what it means
                for APAC in 2026.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>The Global RCS Landscape in 2026.</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Understand how RCS is being adopted across the US, Europe, and
                  leading global markets
                </li>
                <li>
                  See where APAC sits today, and what the next phase of rollout
                  looks like
                </li>
                <li>
                  Gain clarity on timelines, operator readiness, and ecosystem
                  progress
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>See How Leading Brands Are Using RCS.</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Learn how enterprises are driving higher engagement and
                  conversion with RCS
                </li>
                <li>Understand how RCS compares to SMS, WhatsApp, and email</li>
                <li>
                  Explore high-impact use cases across retail, BFSI, travel,
                  logistics, and eCommerce
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Experience RCS in Action.</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Watch a live RCS demo featuring rich media and branded
                  messaging
                </li>
                <li>
                  See how verified senders and conversational journeys build
                  trust
                </li>
                <li>
                  Explore AI-enabled customer interactions in the native
                  messaging inbox
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Prepare for Commercialisation.</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Understand what it takes to launch RCS at scale in APAC</li>
                <li>
                  Learn how to integrate RCS into your existing marketing and CX
                  stack
                </li>
                <li>
                  Take away practical inputs for your 2026 messaging roadmap
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Connect with Industry Experts.</h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Hear directly from Vonage</li>
                <li>
                  Connect with peers shaping the future of business messaging in
                  APAC
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full" id="registration-form">
            <div class="w-full px-6 py-10 sm:py-12 rounded-2xl bg-gray-3">
              <div class="pb-2 sm:pb-4">
                <h2>
                    Thank you
                </h2>
                <h4 class="font-light leading-relaxed">
                    Your subscription has been confirmed. You've been added to our list and will hear from us soon.
                </h4>
              </div>
              <div class="my-4">
                <a href="javascript:history.go('-1')" class="mt-4 w-fit rounded-lg bg-black border-2 border-black px-6 py-3 font-sans text-white font-semibold; hover:bg-transparent hover:text-black focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-5 focus:ring-offset-2; disabled:bg-gray-3 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-colors duration-500" target="_self">
                    Return to page
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <div class="container text-center">
        <div data-usal="fade-u duration-300">
          <h3>Outline Agenda</h3>
          <h4 class="font-bold">
            A structured day of insights, demos, and networking
          </h4>
          <p>
            Agenda is subject to change. Timings and sessions may be adjusted if
            necessary.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-full pt-4 md:pt-6"
          data-usal="fade-u duration-300 delay-200"
        >
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-0 md:gap-4 px-4 py-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-1 transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-nowrap text-sm md:text-base leading-none m-0"
            >
              10:00 - 10:30
            </h4>
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-base md:text-lg leading-none m-0"
            >
              Registration & Welcome Refreshments
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-0 md:gap-4 px-4 py-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-1 transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-nowrap text-sm md:text-base leading-none m-0"
            >
              10:30 - 10:30
            </h4>
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-base md:text-lg leading-none m-0"
            >
              Opening Remarks
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-0 md:gap-4 px-4 py-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-1 transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-nowrap text-sm md:text-base leading-none m-0"
            >
              10:45 - 11:15
            </h4>
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-base md:text-lg leading-none m-0"
            >
              Vonage Global RCS Market Update
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-0 md:gap-4 px-4 py-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-1 transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-nowrap text-sm md:text-base leading-none m-0"
            >
              11:15 - 11:45
            </h4>
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-base md:text-lg leading-none m-0"
            >
              TBA
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-0 md:gap-4 px-4 py-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-1 transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-nowrap text-sm md:text-base leading-none m-0"
            >
              11:45 - 12:00
            </h4>
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-base md:text-lg leading-none m-0"
            >
              Coffee Break
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-0 md:gap-4 px-4 py-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-1 transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-nowrap text-sm md:text-base leading-none m-0"
            >
              12:00 - 12:45
            </h4>
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-base md:text-lg leading-none m-0"
            >
              Vonage Live RCS Demo
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-0 md:gap-4 px-4 py-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-1 transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-nowrap text-sm md:text-base leading-none m-0"
            >
              12:45 - 13:15
            </h4>
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-base md:text-lg leading-none m-0"
            >
              Q&A
            </h4>
          </div>
          <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-0 md:gap-4 px-4 py-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-1 transition-colors duration-500"
          >
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-nowrap text-sm md:text-base leading-none m-0"
            >
              13:15 - 15:00
            </h4>
            <h4
              class="text-black font-semibold text-base md:text-lg leading-none m-0"
            >
              Lunch & Networking
            </h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="bg-linear-to-br from-gray-3/10 via-white to-gray-1 py-20">
      <div
        class="container text-center mySpace-y"
        data-usal="fade-u duration-300"
      >
        <h3>Meet Our Expert Speakers</h3>
        <p>Industry leaders sharing insights on the future of RCS messaging</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:gap-6">
          <!-- Cards 1 -->
          <div
            class="group flex flex-col items-center bg-white pt-4 text-center rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500"
            data-usal="fade-u duration-300 delay-200"
          >
            <div
              class="relative w-[clamp(160px,120px+10vw,208px)] h-[clamp(160px,120px+10vw,208px)] rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-4 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500"
            >
              <Image
                src={speaker1}
                alt="Speaker David Benjamin"
                width="1182"
                height="1330"
                layout="constrained"
                decoding="async"
                loading="lazy"
                class="object-cover w-full h-full"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="w-full rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg md:text-xl mb-1 text-black">
                  David Creasey-Benjamin
                </h4>
                <p
                  class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-5 font-semibold leading-tight mb-1"
                >
                  Strategic Account<br />Manager
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-black font-medium">Vonage</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!--Cards 2-->
          <div
            class="group flex flex-col items-center text-center bg-white pt-4 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-500"
            data-usal="fade-u duration-300 delay-400"
          >
            <div
              class="relative w-[clamp(160px,120px+10vw,208px)] h-[clamp(160px,120px+10vw,208px)] rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-4 shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500"
            >
              <Image
                src={speaker2}
                alt="Speaker Mahendra Mane"
                width="800"
                height="800"
                layout="constrained"
                decoding="async"
                loading="lazy"
                class="object-cover w-full h-full"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="w-full rounded-lg p-4">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg md:text-xl mb-1 text-black">
                  Mahendra Mane
                </h4>
                <p
                  class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-5 font-semibold leading-tight mb-1"
                >
                  Customer Solution <br /> Architect
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-black font-medium">Vonage</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="bg-linear-to-br from-gray-50 via-white to-gray-100 py-10 md:py-20 -my-10 md:-my-20"
    >
      <div class="container text-center mySpace-y">
        <h3>Venue</h3>
        <h4 class="font-bold leading-normal">
          <!-- <a
            href="https://share.google/IEzdmPoZRv4g57Re6"
            target="_blank"
            class="border-b border-black hover:border-transparent transition-colors duration-300 cursor-pointer"
          > -->
            TBC
          </a>
        </h4>
        <p class="w-full md:w-1/2 pb-4 mx-auto">
          Jl. DR. Ide Anak Agung Gde Agung No.1 1, RT.5/RW.2, Kuningan, Mega
          Kuningan, Setiabudi, Jakarta, 12950, Indonesia
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105 aspect-video"
            data-usal="fade-u duration-300"
          >
            <Image
              src={venue1}
              alt="HighHouse Venue View 1"
              width={800}
              layout="constrained"
              class="object-cover w-full h-full"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105 aspect-video"
            data-usal="fade-u duration-300 delay-200"
          >
            <Image
              src={venue2}
              alt="HighHouse Venue View 2"
              width={800}
              layout="constrained"
              class="object-cover w-full h-full"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105 aspect-video"
            data-usal="fade-u duration-300 delay-400"
          >
            <Image
              src={venue3}
              alt="HighHouse Venue View 3"
              width={800}
              layout="constrained"
              class="object-cover w-full h-full"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105 aspect-video"
            data-usal="fade-u duration-300 delay-200"
          >
            <Image
              src={venue4}
              alt="HighHouse Venue View 4"
              width={800}
              layout="constrained"
              class="object-cover w-full h-full"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105 aspect-video"
            data-usal="fade-u duration-300 delay-400"
          >
            <Image
              src={venue5}
              alt="HighHouse Venue View 5"
              width={800}
              layout="constrained"
              class="object-cover w-full h-full"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105 aspect-video"
            data-usal="fade-u duration-300 delay-600"
          >
            <Image
              src={venue6}
              alt="HighHouse Venue View 6"
              width={800}
              layout="constrained"
              class="object-cover w-full h-full"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <footer class="bg-black py-8">
      <div
        class="w-full max-w-5xl px-5 mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center text-center"
      >
        <span class="text-gray-2 text-sm"> © 2026 Vonage </span>
        <span class="text-gray-2 text-sm"> All rights reserved. </span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>
